"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104luj1665702709292.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/luj1665702709292.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/luj1665702709292.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"luj1665702709292\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Help Text\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"luj1665702709292__help_text_315924\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">A Help Text is a legacy Development Object that defines a block of text that is displayed in an application window to provide help about the application. They are unlikely to be used in modern applications.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"luj1665702709292__p_d96191e1_d96192e1_d96193e1\">Help texts must have a unique name; they cannot use the same name as a message.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"luj1665702709292__p_d96194e1_d96195e1_d96196e1\">They can be accessed with the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">help</span> ProcScript statement and the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$text</span> ProcScript function. New and updated help texts are automatically compiled when you save them.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"luj1665702709292__topic_d64277e1_d64278e1_d64279e1_d64280e1_d64281e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d146922e65\">\n                     \n Characteristics\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"luj1665702709292__table_d10679e1_d10680e1_d10681e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"luj1665702709292__table_d10679e1_d10680e1_d10681e1__entry__1\">\n Characteristics\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"luj1665702709292__table_d10679e1_d10680e1_d10681e1__entry__2\"></th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"luj1665702709292__table_d10679e1_d10680e1_d10681e1__entry__1\">\n Object type code:\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"luj1665702709292__table_d10679e1_d10680e1_d10681e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">msg</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"luj1665702709292__table_d10679e1_d10680e1_d10681e1__entry__1\">\n Main Development Object?\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"luj1665702709292__table_d10679e1_d10680e1_d10681e1__entry__2\">\n No\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"luj1665702709292__table_d10679e1_d10680e1_d10681e1__entry__1\">\n Part of:\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"luj1665702709292__table_d10679e1_d10680e1_d10681e1__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ijz1665702550775.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ijz1665702550775.html\" title=\"An Untyped Library is a Main Development Object that defines a collection of objects that may be of different types, and which can be reused or accessed by other objects during development or at runtime.\">Untyped Library</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"luj1665702709292__table_d10679e1_d10680e1_d10681e1__entry__1\">\n Contains:\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"luj1665702709292__table_d10679e1_d10680e1_d10681e1__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jgi1665702550212.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jgi1665702550212.html\" title=\"A Property is a named, typed attribute of Development Object that defines a characteristic or behavior of the object. Each property has a descriptive name, a literal name, a data type, and a value. If no value is specified, a default value may be used.\">Property</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"luj1665702709292__table_d10679e1_d10680e1_d10681e1__entry__1\">\n Generalization:\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"luj1665702709292__table_d10679e1_d10680e1_d10681e1__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ulo1665702550460.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ulo1665702550460.html\" title=\"A Uniface Development Object is an abstract data type that defines the characteristics and behavior of a logical application unit, such as a Component, Field, Message, Library, and so on.\">Development Object</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"luj1665702709292__table_d10679e1_d10680e1_d10681e1__entry__1\">\n Specializations:\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"luj1665702709292__table_d10679e1_d10680e1_d10681e1__entry__2\">\n —\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"luj1665702709292__table_d10679e1_d10680e1_d10681e1__entry__1\">\n Compilation Output:\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"luj1665702709292__table_d10679e1_d10680e1_d10681e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"ph filepath\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">MessageName</var>@<var class=\"keyword varname\">Library</var>@<var class=\"keyword varname\">Language</var>.msg</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"luj1665702709292__table_d10679e1_d10680e1_d10681e1__entry__1\">\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"luj1665702709292__table_d10679e1_d10680e1_d10681e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">lib:<var class=\"keyword varname\">LibraryName.Language</var>:msg:<var class=\"keyword varname\">MessageName</var>\n</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"luj1665702709292__topic_d64282e1_d64283e1_d64284e1_d64285e1_d64286e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d146922e219\"> Specialization </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"luj1665702709292__p_d96203e1_d96204e1_d96205e1\">Help Text specializes Development Object in the\n            following ways:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"luj1665702709292__li_d38960e1_d38961e1_d38962e1\">It has a message library as parent. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"luj1665702709292__li_d38963e1_d38964e1_d38965e1\">It has properties, but no code containers or\n               other development objects. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"luj1665702709292__li_d38966e1_d38967e1_d38968e1\">Unlike Message objects, it has window dimensions.\n            </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614454\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614454\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Help Text Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Help Text A Help Text is a legacy Development Object that defines a block of text that is displayed in an application window to provide help about the application. They are unlikely to be used in modern applications. Help texts must have a unique name; they cannot use the same name as a message. They can be accessed with the help ProcScript statement and the $text ProcScript function. New and updated help texts are automatically compiled when you save them. Characteristics Characteristics Object type code: msg Main Development Object? No Part of: Untyped Library Contains: Property Generalization: Development Object Specializations: — Compilation Output: MessageName @ Library @ Language .msg lib: LibraryName.Language :msg: MessageName Specialization Help Text specializes Development Object in the following ways: It has a message library as parent. It has properties, but no code containers or other development objects. Unlike Message objects, it has window dimensions. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}